.archive.org/web/20110723153707/http://cbdr.cmu.edu/event.asp?eventID=15\">Emily Pronin, Center for Behavioral Decision Research</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Scopelliti2015-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-Scopelliti2015_3-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-Scopelliti2015_3-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-Scopelliti2015_3-2\"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite id=\"CITEREFScopellitiMorewedgeMcCormickMin2015\" class=\"citation journal cs1\">Scopelliti, Irene; Morewedge, Carey K.; McCormick, Erin; Min, H. Lauren; Lebrecht, Sophie; Kassam, Karim S. (2015). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.1287/mnsc.2014.2096\">\"Bias Blind Spot: Structure, Measurement, and Consequences\"</a>. <i><a href=\"https://wikipedia.com/wiki/Management_Science_(journal)\" title=\"Management Science (journal)\">Management Science</a></i>. <b>61</b> (10): 2468–2486. <a href=\"https://wikipedia.com/wiki/Doi_(identifier)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Doi (identifier)\">doi</a>:<span class=\"cs1-lock-free\" title=\"Freely accessible\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.1287%2Fmnsc.2014.2096\">10.1287/mnsc.2014.2096</a></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Management+Science&amp;rft.atitle=Bias+Blind+Spot%3A+Structure%2C+Measurement%2C+and+Consequences&amp;rft.volume=61&amp;rft.issue=10&amp;rft.pages=2468-2486&amp;rft.date=2015&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1287%2Fmnsc.2014.2096&amp;rft.aulast=Scopelliti&amp;rft.aufirst=Irene&amp;rft.au=Morewedge%2C+Carey+K.&amp;rft.au=McCormick%2C+Erin&amp;rft.au=Min%2C+H.+Lauren&amp;rft.au=Lebrecht%2C+Sophie&amp;rft.au=Kassam%2C+Karim+S.&amp;rft_id=%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1287%2Fmnsc.2014.2096&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABias+blind+spot\" class=\"Z3988\"></span><link re